                    "id": "nexoos-head-of-product-data-investor-wallet",
                    "name": "Fixing the Last Mile of Investing: Designing an Investor Wallet for Nexoos",
                    "narrative": "Replaced Nexoos’s broken invest-then-transfer flow with a pre-funded wallet. Investors deposit in advance, invest instantly, receive repayments back automatically. Waiting-list recall rate dropped from 10% to 0%. Created a reinvestment loop.",
                    "results": "",
