                    "id": "nexoos-head-of-product-data-funding-channel-sorting-hat",
                    "name": "Funding Channel Sorting Hat: Designing a Fair Allocation System at Nexoos",
                    "narrative": "Built a rule-based allocation service (“Sorting Hat”) to distribute approved loans fairly between retail marketplace and institutional debenture portfolios. Evaluated each loan on size, industry, risk, and concentration factors. Created auditable, balanced, transparent allocation as Nexoos evolved into a multi-channel lender.",
                    "results": "",
