                    "name": "When Not to Scale: What We Learned from Incubating iRent at QuintoAndar",
                    "narrative": "Incubated iBuyer-inspired rental model (iRent): QuintoAndar guarantees rent to owner, re-rents at a margin. Discovered structural adverse selection—owners accepted when we overpriced, rejected when we underpriced. Viable only in narrow high-data geographies. Shelved—a high-quality decision avoiding a structurally fragile business.",
