                    "narrative": "Transformed QuintoAndar’s for-sale marketplace from a rental clone into a sales engine. Fixed agent continuity for buyers, then used the Casa Mineira acquisition to redesign the full operating model: agent specialization, lead allocation, buyer qualification, commission logic. Combined brokerage craft with marketplace technology. Signed contracts grew 9x in one year.",
