                    "narrative": "First LLM product at QuintoAndar; built on the earlier Search, Qualification, and Quality thesis (defined qualified search, unified UI, geographic retrieval). Conversational search with voice + visual retrieval; agent preserved qualification rules. Dynamic listing covers by query. Modest conversion lift (strongest in sales); built LLM muscle + internal AI platform + strong innovation narrative.",
